<para>Update for jsoneditor.googlecode.com for Qt 5.3</para>

<para></para>

<para><formalpara><title>Features </title></formalpara>
</para>

<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Open, Save, SaveAs</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Find, Find and Replace</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Syntax Highlighting</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Editing on Tree view on the right</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Formatting/Pretty Print of <link linkend="namespace_json">Json</link></para>
</listitem><listitem>
